fields.fld-constraints-notes:
{"constraint":"Priya repeated that the pilot phase is intentionally narrow"}
{"constraint":"This redundancy not only frustrated customers, but also gradually eroded the confidence of new agents who still struggled to maintain context as they switched between tools"}
{"constraint":"Each interaction required the agent to rebuild the entire story from scratch because the customer’s earlier messages were siloed in systems that did not synchronize"}
{"constraint":"Because the pilot period was narrow by design, the team needed to ensure the core experience behaved reliably at all times, even if some advanced features remained aspirational"}

fields.fld-dependencies-notes:
{"dependency":"The focus of this phase is to get the core platform working correctly before adding advanced features later"}
{"dependency":"Shortly after, there will be a short prototyping sprint to build a simple but interactive workspace shell that includes communication placeholders and working keyboard navigation"}
